name: Attack
note:
Skill #1 will be used when you select
the Attack command.

<setup action>
display action
immortal: targets, true
</setup action>

<target action>
if user.attackMotion() !== 'missile'
  move user: targets, front, 20
else
  perform start
end
wait for movement
perform action
attack animation: target
wait for animation
action effect
</target action>
